1. Open terminal

2. Initialize git (first time only)
   git init

3. Add files
   git add .

4. Save changes
   git commit -m "Day 1 - Backend setup and products API"

5. Main branch set (first time only)
   git branch -M main

6. Connect GitHub repository
   git remote add origin YOUR_GITHUB_LINK

7. Push code
   git push -u origin main





   explanation


   git init
→ yo folder lai Git project banaucha

